\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 Core Concept\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 The app's unique value proposition is 
\f1\b learning from YOUR content
\f0\b0  rather than generic curriculum. Instead of HSK word lists, the app builds a personal frequency corpus from text you actually encounter, then prioritizes flashcards accordingly. Existing apps like Pleco and PinyinOCR handle OCR well, but none close the loop by turning your personal exposure into a prioritized learning queue.play.google+1\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

