\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 Development Log\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 2026-03-12 \'97 Core MVP\
\f0\b0 Full stack built and running locally. Backend: FastAPI + PostgreSQL + SQLAlchemy async (asyncpg driver). Schema:
\f2\fs22 cedict
\f0\fs24  (~120k CC-CEDICT entries, read-only),
\f2\fs22 words
\f0\fs24  (user corpus),
\f2\fs22 encounters
\f0\fs24  (append-only log),
\f2\fs22 pages
\f0\fs24  (analyzed pages). Custom SM-2 SRS in
\f2\fs22 backend/app/services/srs.py
\f0\fs24 . Priority score formula:
\f2\fs22 (encounter_count \uc0\u215  source_diversity_count) / familiarity_score
\f0\fs24  (unknowns use 0.5 as denominator to float to top).\

Chrome MV3 extension captures page text (8000 char limit), calls Claude Haiku (
\f2\fs22 claude-haiku-4-5-20251001
\f0\fs24 , temp=0, max_tokens=1500) for word extraction, and POSTs to
\f2\fs22 /api/ingest
\f0\fs24 . All extension state in
\f2\fs22 chrome.storage.local
\f0\fs24  (MV3 service workers are ephemeral). API key + backend URL configurable via Options page.\

Frontend dashboard (served at
\f2\fs22 /static/index.html
\f0\fs24 ): vocabulary list with filter/sort, inline familiarity buttons, priority bar visualization, context sentence expansion. Flashcard review system with two modes: (1) AI-generated daily study plan via
\f2\fs22 /api/study/plan
\f0\fs24 , (2) Free Study with Sight Reading and \'93Worth Another Look\'94 decks. Pinyin tone color-coding throughout. Optimistic UI updates with server sync rollback on error.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b 2026-03-12 \'97 Stroke-Order Animation\
\f0\b0 Replaced freehand canvas drawing (impractical on trackpad) with animated stroke-order playback using the
\f2\fs22 hanzi-writer
\f0\fs24  CDN library (v3.5). Flow when \'93Still Learning\'94 is clicked: character strokes animate automatically \uc0\u8594  user replays as desired \u8594  clicks \'93I wrote it\'94 \u8594  character blurs for recall phase \u8594  \'93Done Practicing\'94 advances to next card. Multi-character words split into individual CJK characters, each with its own writer instance, animated sequentially. Rare or unsupported characters show a graceful fallback message; practice remains completable via Skip. State simplified: removed
\f2\fs22 traceCount
\f0\fs24 , phase changed from
\f2\fs22 \'91trace\'94|\'91recall\'94
\f0\fs24  to
\f2\fs22 \'91watch\'94|\'91recall\'94
\f0\fs24 . Only
\f2\fs22 backend/static/index.html
\f0\fs24  changed.\
